Package com.binance.api.client.domain.market

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AggTrade
    An aggregated trade event for a symbol.
    BookTicker
    Represents the best price/qty on the order book for a given symbol.
    Candlestick
    Kline/Candlestick bars for a symbol.
    OrderBook
    Order book of a symbol in Binance.
    OrderBookEntry
    An order book entry consisting of price and quantity.
    OrderBookEntryDeserializer
    Custom deserializer for an OrderBookEntry, since the API returns an array in the format [ price, qty, [] ].
    OrderBookEntrySerializer
    Custom serializer for an OrderBookEntry.
    TickerPrice
    Wraps a symbol and its corresponding latest price.
    TickerStatistics
    24 hour price change statistics for a ticker.
